@grand_coalition_prussia
title: We can form a Grand Coalition.
view-if: grand_coalition_prussia >= 50 and grand_coalition_prussia_failed == 0
subtitle: SPD + Z + [? if ddp_exist: [+ ddp_name +] + ?] [+ dvp_name +] ([+ grand_coalition_prussia +]%)
go-to: grand_coalition_prussia_success if spd_relation >= 45 and dvp_ideology = "Left"; grand_coalition_prussia_failed if not (spd_relation >= 45 and dvp_ideology = "Left")

We will ask the SPD to include us in Prussian Government.

@grand_coalition_prussia_success
on-arrival: in_grand_coalition_prussia = 1; spd_prussia = 1; dvp_prussia = 1; prussia_leader = "Braun"; liberal_strength += 5;

The SPD has agreed to form a Grand Coalition!

@grand_coalition_prussia_failed
on-arrival: in_grand_coalition_prussia = 0; grand_coalition_prussia_failed = 1;
go-to: coalition_menu

The SPD has refused to form a Grand Coalition.



@no_majority
title: There is no clear governing majority.
view-if: weimar_coalition_prussia < 50 and (grand_coalition_prussia < 50 or grand_coalition_prussia_failed == 1)
on-arrival: next_election_time_prussia = time+3; next_election_month_prussia = month + 3; next_election_year_prussia = year; next_election_year_prussia += 1 if next_election_month_prussia > 12; next_election_month_prussia -= 12 if next_election_month_prussia > 12;
